<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kids Wellness Tales - Healthy Stories for Children</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', 'Trebuchet MS', cursive, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            animation: slideDown 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .stories-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .story-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .story-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .story-emoji {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .story-card h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }

        .story-card .category {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .story-card p {
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1em;
        }

        .story-card .wellness-tip {
            background: #f0f4ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #555;
        }

        .story-card .wellness-tip strong {
            color: #667eea;
        }

        .read-more {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .read-more:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .wellness-section {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .wellness-section h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2em;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #764ba2;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .wellness-tips {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .tip-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .tip-box:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .tip-box .icon {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .tip-box h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        @keyframes slideDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }

            .stories-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            header p {
                font-size: 1em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>🌈 Kids Wellness Tales</h1>
            <p>Happy, Healthy Stories for Growing Kids</p>
        </header>

        <div class="stories-grid">
            <!-- Story 1: Mindful Breathing -->
            <div class="story-card">
                <div class="story-emoji">🧘‍♀️</div>
                <h2>Luna's Calm Breath</h2>
                <span class="category">Mindfulness</span>
                <p>
                    Luna the bunny learns that when she feels anxious about starting school, 
                    she can take deep breaths like a balloon filling with air and slowly letting 
                    it out. This simple breathing trick helps her feel calm and ready for anything!
                </p>
                <div class="wellness-tip">
                    <strong>Wellness Tip:</strong> Try the 4-7-8 breathing: Breathe in for 4 counts, 
                    hold for 7, and breathe out for 8.
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="read-more">Read Full Story →</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Story 2: Physical Activity -->
            <div class="story-card">
                <div class="story-emoji">🐢</div>
                <h2>Terry the Turtle's Adventure</h2>
                <span class="category">Exercise</span>
                <p>
                    Terry the turtle discovers that moving his body makes him feel energized and happy. 
                    From dancing to hiking, he learns that exercise is not boring—it's an adventure! 
                    Join him as he finds joy in staying active.
                </p>
                <div class="wellness-tip">
                    <strong>Wellness Tip:</strong> Try to move your body for at least 30 minutes 
                    a day. It can be playing, dancing, or any activity you enjoy!
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="read-more">Read Full Story →</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Story 3: Healthy Eating -->
            <div class="story-card">
                <div class="story-emoji">🍎</div>
                <h2>Oliver's Rainbow Plate</h2>
                <span class="category">Nutrition</span>
                <p>
                    Oliver the owl learns that eating a variety of colorful foods gives his body 
                    superpowers! Red tomatoes, orange carrots, yellow bananas, and more—each color 
                    has special nutrients to keep him healthy and strong.
                </p>
                <div class="wellness-tip">
                    <strong>Wellness Tip:</strong> Eat the rainbow! Try to include fruits and 
                    vegetables of different colors in each meal.
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="read-more">Read Full Story →</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Story 4: Sleep & Rest -->
            <div class="story-card">
                <div class="story-emoji">😴</div>
                <h2>Sophie's Sleepy-Time Song</h2>
                <span class="category">Sleep</span>
                <p>
                    Sophie the squirrel didn't like bedtime until she discovered her own special 
                    routine! A warm drink, a cozy blanket, and a gentle song help her drift off 
                    to dreamland feeling safe and rested.
                </p>
                <div class="wellness-tip">
                    <strong>Wellness Tip:</strong> Create a bedtime routine! Try reading, soft music, 
                    or a warm bath before sleep.
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="read-more">Read Full Story →</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Story 5: Emotional Well-being -->
            <div class="story-card">
                <div class="story-emoji">💚</div>
                <h2>Bella's Feelings Garden</h2>
                <span class="category">Emotions</span>
                <p>
                    Bella the butterfly learns that all feelings are okay and normal—happiness, sadness, 
                    anger, and worry. Like flowers in a garden, each emotion has its own beauty and 
                    teaches us something important.
                </p>
                <div class="wellness-tip">
                    <strong>Wellness Tip:</strong> It's okay to feel different emotions. Talk to someone 
                    you trust about how you're feeling.
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="read-more">Read Full Story →</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Story 6: Friendship & Kindness -->
            <div class="story-card">
                <div class="story-emoji">🤝</div>
                <h2>Max's Kindness Quest</h2>
                <span class="category">Social Wellness</span>
                <p>
                    Max the mouse discovers that small acts of kindness create big happiness. 
                    Whether sharing a snack, helping a friend, or giving a hug, he learns that 
                    being kind makes his whole community feel better.
                </p>
                <div class="wellness-tip">
                    <strong>Wellness Tip:</strong> Do one small act of kindness today! It might 
                    make someone's day better.
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="read-more">Read Full Story →</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Wellness Tips Section -->
        <div class="wellness-section">
            <h2>✨ Daily Wellness Reminders</h2>
            <div class="wellness-tips">
                <div class="tip-box">
                    <div class="icon">💧</div>
                    <h3>Stay Hydrated</h3>
                    <p>Drink plenty of water throughout the day to keep your body happy!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tip-box">
                    <div class="icon">🌞</div>
                    <h3>Get Sunshine</h3>
                    <p>Spend time outside for Vitamin D and fresh air every day.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tip-box">
                    <div class="icon">🧠</div>
                    <h3>Think Positive</h3>
                    <p>Notice good things around you and practice gratitude daily.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tip-box">
                    <div class="icon">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</div>
                    <h3>Connect & Share</h3>
                    <p>Spend quality time with family and friends you care about.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2026 Kids Wellness Tales. Created with 💚 to help children grow healthy and happy.</p>
            <p>Remember: You are amazing just the way you are!</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
